'''Taq Tavi''' ({{lang-fa|<U+0637><U+0627><U+0642> <U+062A><U+0627><U+0648><U+064A>}}, also [[Romanize]]d as '''<U+0162><U+0101>q T<U+0101>v<U+012B>''' and '''<U+0162><U+0101>q<U+0163><U+0101>v<U+012B>''')<ref>{{GEOnet3|-3846387|Taq Tavi}}</ref> is a village in [[Arkavazi Rural District]], [[Chavar District]], [[Ilam County]], [[Ilam Province]], [[Iran]]. At the 2006 census, its population was 13, in 4 families.<ref>{{IranCensus2006|16}}</ref>  

